Why Dodge Is First to Flip the Switch
It might seem surprising that Dodge, the most old-school of the Detroit Three, is rst out the

Dodges advantages:

The Cultural Dilemma: Enthusiast Backlash
Not everyones sold on the electric future of muscle. Many diehard fans see EVs as soulless,

Common cricisms:

Sll, theres a growing Gen Z and Millennial audience that sees EVs as normal or even

Are EV Muscle Cars Here to Stay or Just a Phase?
Whether or not EV muscle cars are the future depends on several variables:
